OL,3,CHomelessness charities under extra
OL,4,Cstrain as demand rises
OL,6,FTwo of Jersey's largest homelessness
OL,7,Fcharities say their services are being
OL,8,Fplaced under increasing strain from
OL,9,Fgrowing demand.
OL,11,FIt comes after the Shelter Trust's
OL,12,Fannual 'Tinathon' received a record
OL,13,Fnumber of donations, with 13,000 tins
OL,14,Fcollected for those in need.
OL,16,FAs well as supplying kitchens across
OL,17,Fthe charity's seven homeless shelters,
OL,18,Fthey are also used in food parcels for
OL,19,Fthose struggling to make ends meet.
