OL,6,FRichard Robins, organiser of the
OL,7,FTinathon, says: "Demand continues to
OL,8,Fincrease and times are hard for a lot
OL,9,Fof people, so those food parcels mean
OL,10,Fa lot."
OL,12,FHe adds that whilst many people do not
OL,13,Ffeel as though there is a significant
OL,14,Fhomelessness problem on the island, it
OL,15,Fstill exists.
OL,17,FRichard explains: "It is definitely a
OL,18,Fhidden issue and one of the purposes
OL,19,Fof an event like the Tinathon is to
OL,20,Fmake people aware that it is still a
OL,21,Fproblem in Jersey.
