OL,3,CHomelessness charities under extra
OL,4,Cstrain as demand rises
OL,6,F"I have no doubt that numbers (of
OL,7,Fhomeless people) are on the rise."
OL,9,FTim Ringsdore, Chief Executive Officer
OL,10,Fof the Sanctuary Trust, another local
OL,11,Fhomelessness charity, agrees.
OL,13,FHe says: "Unfortunately, the problem
OL,14,Fisn't going away.
OL,16,F"There's currently over 340 people
OL,17,Fdesignated homeless and we can only
OL,18,Fsupport a few of those people, up to
OL,19,F30 men at any one time.
