OL,3,CHomelessness charities under extra
OL,4,Cstrain as demand rises
OL,6,F"There's lots of people that we don't
OL,7,Fknow about too. There's people sofa
OL,8,Fsurfing, living in their cars, in
OL,9,Ftheir vans, and obviously multi-
OL,10,Fdwellings as well. So there's actually
OL,11,Fa lot more of a challenge in the
OL,12,Fisland than people think."
OL,14,FThe charity's Operations Manager, Jack
OL,15,FSlater, adds: "The chief problem that
OL,16,Fwe see is mental health, we believe
OL,17,Fit's one of the primary drivers of
OL,18,Fhomelessness.
OL,20,F"Particularly post-COVID, there's been
OL,21,Fa gradual increase in demand.
