OL,6,F"Jersey's a very affluent island but
OL,7,Fthat also means it's a very expensive
OL,8,Fisland, so coinciding with the cost of
OL,9,Fliving, inflation, particularly the
OL,10,Fcost of housing and rent are
OL,11,Fcompletely unsustainable for a lot of
OL,12,Fpeople."
